	&lt;li&gt;In its current form, the patch will need some modifications to work with 0.90 because HBA doesn&apos;t have a close method.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Still not thrilled with scan/rescan of table attributes for transformation directives, in retrospect.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

